txt.en: Half-orcs are not the only servants of Saruman riding through the fields of the Broadacres. Goblin-skirmishers ravage the landscape, burning the grazing lands. You should defeat the goblin-skirmishers who scout the plains near Oserley.
Goblin-skirmishers can be found in the fields west of Oserley.\n\nYou should defeat the goblin-skirmishers harassing Oserley.
